fillets-ng:  Fish Fillets NG is strictly a puzzle game. The goal in every of 
fillets-ng:  the seventy levels is always the same: find a safe way out. The 
fillets-ng:  fish utter witty remarks about their surroundings, the various 
fillets-ng:  inhabitants of their underwater realm quarrel among themselves 
fillets-ng:  or comment on the efforts of your fish. The whole game is 
fillets-ng:  accompanied by quiet, comforting music.
